# Iris Flower Classification

This project classifies Iris flowers into different species using machine learning.

## Dataset
Iris Dataset from sklearn

## Tools & Libraries
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Google Colab

## Model Used
- Logistic Regression

## Workflow
1. Load Iris dataset
2. Data preprocessing
3. Train-test split
4. Model training
5. Evaluation using accuracy score

## Results
- The model achieved high accuracy due to the clean and well-structured dataset.
- Accuracy obtained: 1.0

